        public List<AttributeMap> getUserAttributes()
        Description copied from interface: UsersResponseContext
        Get the list of user attributes generated for an Identity Store Provisioner operation.

        At a minimum, each map in the returned list must contain the following attributes:

        • Constants.ID
        • Constants.WHEN_CHANGED
        • Constants.WHEN_CREATED
